quote><blockquote><blockquote>CE AL改制DSE己經睇到呢班人幾短視</blockquote><br />\n短視？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不知幾遠視<br />\n人地dse六年為同大陸接軌呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n好遠視咁配合一系列既種族清洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n同埋有系統地殖民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91cdca31833390421bcbfbca4ecc8f62fe9fce30","tid":193064,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:56:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從唔敢用 linux 已經反映緊香港教育水平</blockquote><br />\nA神竟然無人回<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7494aa7ac46c8af26e5b0f031ab7fff15d2087d2","tid":193064,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:58:46.000Z","msg":"無人理條友"},{"pid":"0c6eb7bbb40575116c8d67197d024ea42d97c88d","tid":193064,"uid":47774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T00:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>從唔敢用 linux 已經反映緊香港教育水平</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b7922b96038f3d8ff06067a3f178f9f1958d329","tid":193064,"uid":4934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:02:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>從唔敢用 linux 已經反映緊香港教育水平</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}